name: ONE of ONE of ONE | ISSUE 3/4
description:
this is your wallet identifier represented by a series of seemingly random glyphs across the range of colours made available to us by nature; if you look carefully enough you will see that it contains the colour of every plant, of every flower, of every creature, and of every other point in time and space, past and present, forever frozen across this prismatic plane of existence

gaze into the beauty of the unknown, and marvel at the myriad of options available to us. when faced with choices that lie ahead of you, which path will you choose, and how will that choice impact your next decision at the next fork?

this unique 1/1 goes a step further by adding an additional dimension, ensuring each viewer has their own unique, persistent version of this nft, essentially turning it into a 1/1/1 edition
